content.speaker: Mr. SPANO
content.text:
Mr. SPANO. Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to be removed as 
cosponsor of H.J. Res. 25.

content.speaker: The SPEAKER pro tempore
content.text:
The SPEAKER pro tempore. Is there objection to the request of the 
gentleman from Florida?

doc_title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.J. RES. 25
